PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1774271469
OL,3,CTributes grow as friends killed in
OL,4,Ccrash named
OL,6,FIt said: "Corey previously played at
OL,7,FSiddal, and rugby was always a big
OL,8,Fpart of his life. Our thoughts are
OL,9,Fwith everyone affected at this
OL,10,Fincredibly difficult time.
OL,12,F"We send our love to Corey's family
OL,13,Fand all who knew him."
OL,15,FHalifax MP Kate Dearden said the
OL,16,Fincident was "devastating news".
OL,18,FShe said: "My thoughts are with their
OL,19,Ffamilies and friends at this
OL,20,Fincredibly difficult time, and with
OL,21,Fthe young man who remains in hospital.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
