OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1774271469
OL,3,CTributes grow as friends killed in
OL,4,Ccrash named
OL,6,F"This will be felt right across the
OL,7,Fcommunity."
OL,9,FLocal councillor Shane Taylor added:
OL,10,F"There's genuine shock and sadness in
OL,11,Fthe community, there's a lot of grief.
OL,13,F"It's talked about in the shops, it's
OL,14,Fon social media. It goes to show how
OL,15,Fthis can affect a community. Even the
OL,16,Flocal church today is packed out,
OL,17,Fthere's a condolence book.
OL,19,F"Last night we had hundreds of people
OL,20,Fat a vigil."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
