OL,3,CTributes grow as friends killed in
OL,4,Ccrash named
OL,6,FTwo women, aged 18 and 32, who were
OL,7,Falso arrested, are continuing to
OL,8,Freceive treatment for their injuries
OL,9,Fbut are no longer under arrest, West
OL,10,FYorkshire Police said.
OL,12,FThe force said another man, aged 26
OL,13,Fand from Bradford, has been arrested
OL,14,Fon suspicion of causing death by
OL,15,Fdangerous driving.
OL,17,FOfficers say they are carrying out
OL,18,Fenquiries about a vehicle not directly
OL,19,Finvolved in the collision which was in
OL,20,Fthe area at the time.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
